{"tid":1322800,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【荃葵大遊行】8964，兩萬人荃葵長征","createTime":"2019-07-16T05:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T09:33:27.000Z","uid":121784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0af703e1451d6c5a1929d0b84cdfc1f40394eb1c","tid":1322800,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:02:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C/334221/%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B%E4%B8%89%E5%8D%81-%E5%85%A9%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E8%8D%83%E8%91%B5%E9%95%B7%E5%BE%81-%E4%B8%80%E4%BD%8D%E8%A1%97%E5%9D%8A%E8%B8%8F%E4%B8%8A%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B%E8%A8%98%E6%86%B6%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%B8%E8%B7%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A1%258C%2F334221%2F%25E5%2585%25AD%25E5%259B%259B%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%258D%2581-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%258D%2583%25E8%2591%25B5%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25BE%2581-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25BD%258D%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%259D%258A%25E8%25B8%258F%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%2585%25AD%25E5%259B%259B%25E8%25A8%2598%25E6%2586%25B6%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E8%25B7%25AF&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXmrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=2ebae95c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C/334221/%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B%E4%B8%89%E5%8D%81-%E5%85%A9%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E8%8D%83%E8%91%B5%E9%95%B7%E5%BE%81-%E4%B8%80%E4%BD%8D%E8%A1%97%E5%9D%8A%E8%B8%8F%E4%B8%8A%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B%E8%A8%98%E6%86%B6%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%B8%E8%B7%AF</a><br />\n<br />\n「我問自己仲可以做咩？」八九民運，軍隊開槍射殺平民學生一幕，舉世震驚，荃灣街坊鄺國全，當時這樣反問自己。自此，他由一位小學教師，毅然從政，當了16年區議員，「荃葵當年係屬於民主派系統」。每年五、六月，他都會把珍藏的八九民運相片集帶回學校，薪火相傳。<br />\n<br />\n這位荃灣老街坊的六四故事，要從30年前五月的荃灣環市大遊行說起。每當提及八九民運與香港關係，我們總會想起1989年5月28日的「百五萬環島大遊行」。 其實，當日集會遊行亦在全港遍地開花。《文匯報》當年曾推算屯門、葵青、北區、沙田有達十萬人參與地區遊行。荃灣、葵青兩區街坊更曾出現跨區長征，遙遙支援2,000公里外的八九民運。<br />\n葵青區議員梁耀忠憶述：「街坊會自發拎布寫橫額，同我哋搞反加租好唔同」。鄺國全也說：「當時逼爆沙咀道球場」。六四30周年，兩位地區政壇老將，為荃葵區街坊說一段30年來，鮮被鎂光燈關愛的香港八九回憶。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;由二十二位荃灣、葵青區議員發起響應北京學生呼籲進行的大遊行，於昨日下午分別由葵芳及荃灣沙咀道球場出發，兩區遊行隊伍在德士古道匯合，組成龐大隊伍，環繞荃灣市中心遊行，人數達二萬多人，圍觀者亦數萬。<br />\n<br />\n《大公報》，1989年5月29日&rdquo;"},{"pid":"e86e94805ba1ce99ba2445410fc1247469f51bc2","tid":1322800,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:47:35.000Z","msg":"荃灣啲蝗係150定自由行黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />d look 好鬼鄕下"},{"pid":"3bbf70a1fa4a27c9577e2447c470300d858928d5","tid":1322800,"uid":195493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:49:21.000Z","msg":"點解而家荃葵會咁藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0193d96b0b4ac407303f50855f92bbb88062f0","tid":1322800,"uid":116709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3bbf70a1fa4a27c9577e2447c470300d858928d5","tid":1322800,"uid":195493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:49:21.000Z","msg":"點解而家荃葵會咁藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:15:46.000Z","msg":"多癈老"},{"pid":"a9d56dc664b455cc30621ba8fa195d5e6ba70c41","tid":1322800,"uid":121784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d0193d96b0b4ac407303f50855f92bbb88062f0","tid":1322800,"uid":116709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3bbf70a1fa4a27c9577e2447c470300d858928d5","tid":1322800,"uid":195493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:49:21.000Z","msg":"點解而家荃葵會咁藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:15:46.000Z","msg":"多癈老"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:29:58.000Z","msg":"社區老化"},{"pid":"1377b5f63707e36e2099a1258b24c1c31334468d","tid":1322800,"uid":121784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:31:40.000Z","msg":"三十年後，大公報都不再平反六四"},{"pid":"0ef9533e0b80971de082ffd65d2b65fd2f403df5","tid":1322800,"uid":35112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s